    "description": "Forge your path in The InBetween, an emotional story-driven metroidvania. You play as a Pipit, a young boy whose fate, as well as that of an underground world lies in your actions and choices.<br><br><strong>&quot;...you've met with a terrible fate, haven't you?&quot;</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050000/extras/9204d39ecda49aca310b3d80110308c7.poster.avif?t=1759919242\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050000/extras/9204d39ecda49aca310b3d80110308c7.webm?t=1759919242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050000/extras/9204d39ecda49aca310b3d80110308c7.mp4?t=1759919242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The InBetween is a gut-wrenching yet wholesome 2d hand-drawn/pixel art metroidvania where your <strong>F</strong>ate as well as an infected underground world lies in your skills and your conscience.<br><br><strong>Seek the Vir’s source…</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050000/extras/db7e2606555c115566e973e6c5e212d8.poster.avif?t=1759919242\" width=480 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050000/extras/db7e2606555c115566e973e6c5e212d8.webm?t=1759919242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050000/extras/db7e2606555c115566e973e6c5e212d8.mp4?t=1759919242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The world of Aija has been infested with VIR and monsters manifested from it. Elim<strong><i>i</i></strong>nate them all down to their source with your trusty blaster and assortment of special attacks and abilities.<br><br><strong>Decide your fate....</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050000/extras/1225898ee33c2323e91e478011ab18ee.poster.avif?t=1759919242\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050000/extras/1225898ee33c2323e91e478011ab18ee.webm?t=1759919242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050000/extras/1225898ee33c2323e91e478011ab18ee.mp4?t=1759919242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore the world of Aija, filled with i<strong>N</strong>fected people. And it’s up to you to either heal them or eliminate them. Through a combination of fast-paced gunplay and Undertale-inspired turn-based battles.<br><br><strong>Face The Consequences…</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050000/extras/4ee7bc63b2ee56f9a0c99a121e53a643.poster.avif?t=1759919242\" width=600 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050000/extras/4ee7bc63b2ee56f9a0c99a121e53a643.webm?t=1759919242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050000/extras/4ee7bc63b2ee56f9a0c99a121e53a643.mp4?t=1759919242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Your actions get judge<strong>D</strong> and you face the consequences in multiple endings.<br>Will you be the Hero? The Villain?<br>Or somewhere InBetween?<br><br><strong>Uncover The Truth....</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050000/extras/39971203cc7441dd4673d3f7338067bb.poster.avif?t=1759919242\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050000/extras/39971203cc7441dd4673d3f7338067bb.webm?t=1759919242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3050000/extras/39971203cc7441dd4673d3f7338067bb.mp4?t=1759919242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There are a lot of questions that remain unanswered lying within and beyond the real<strong>M</strong> of Aija.<br>Will you be up to the task of uncovering the mystery within and beyond the gam<strong>E</strong>'s story?",
